import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import tw from 'twin.macro'

const PageContainer = styled.div`
    ${tw`
        flex
        flex-col
        w-full 
        h-full 
        items-center 
        overflow-x-hidden
    `}
`;

export function HomePage() {
    return <PageContainer>
        Hello world
    </PageContainer>
}
